{"tid":2022372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長洲34歲仔墮樓跌坐街中 母親報警清醒送院","createTime":"2020-05-18T09:41:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T10:09:53.000Z","uid":229185,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"566eee261e33e4c8b190907c8219cc62bd490dd1","tid":2022372,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T09:41:08.000Z","msg":"好彩無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名34歲男子早上在長洲高處墮下，跌坐中興新街，清醒送長洲醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n警方早上8時45分接獲事主的53歲母親報案，指發現兒子坐在中興新街29號對開，懷疑從高處墮下企圖自殺。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場，事主清醒被送往長洲醫院治理，警方於現場沒有檢獲遺書，初步調查相信事主於一樓層墮下，事件沒有可疑。"},{"pid":"4efbd113ad1273781b2499f85681815965f6cdaa","tid":2022372,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T09:43:00.000Z","msg":"一樓墜下，遺書？"},{"pid":"a58e87c392d0920b163535d1e054a29446b55350","tid":2022372,"uid":29070,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T09:59:30.000Z","msg":"邊位巴打"},{"pid":"440f2ee2a64bd26e9f380650fa0ea02902fcdc85","tid":2022372,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T10:09:53.000Z","msg":"53 ? 34 ?"}]}